*   **It closes the circuit:** Where a flat constant applied to a 3D volume leaves an open load ($\pi = \text{OL}$), the string verb resolves cleanly[span_19](start_span)[span_19](end_span). The measurement terminates because the operational tool is perfectly matched to the dimensional container[span_20](start_span)[span_20](end_span).

